## 2) Cerca i filtres potents
Comandes i opcions útils:
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">find &lt;RUTA> -type f -name "*.log" -size +10M -mtime -7 -delete`</kbd>
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">locate nginx.conf</kbd> (*cal* <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">updatedb</kbd> prèviament en algunes distros)
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">grep -Rin --color=never "usb" .</kbd> (recursiu (**`R`**), insensible a majúscules (**`i`**), n° de línia (**`n`**))
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">head<span style="background-color: white; color: black;">, </span>tail -n 50<span style="background-color: white; color: black;">, </span>tail -f fitxer.log</kbd> (seguiment en temps real)
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">cut -d: -f1 /etc/passwd</kbd> (columns)
- <kbd style="background-color:LightGrey; color: blue;">sort<span style="background-color: white; color: black;">, </span>uniq -c<span style="background-color: white; color: black;">, </span>wc -l<span style="background-color: white; color: black;">, </span>xargs</kbd>

----

